title: Train hero Spencer Stone's condition improves as Calif. police ask: What led to stabbing?
text:
Train hero Spencer Stone's condition improves as Calif. police ask: What led to stabbing? 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
Airman 1st Class Spencer Stone, 23, "is awake, able to get out of bed and in good spirits," the hospital said in a statement....
